<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>ZptSharp error</title>
<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 1em;
  font-family: sans-serif;
  line-height: 140%;
}
body>header {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #DAA;
  padding: 0 0 0.8em;
  margin: 0 0 1em;
}
h1 {
  margin: 0;
  color: #600;
  font-size: 250%;
  line-height: 100%;
}
p {
  margin: 0 0 0.4em;
}
.user_message {
  font-size: 110%;
  line-height: 140%;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 2em 0 3em;
}
.tech_info {
  background: #F0F0F0;
  padding: 1em;
}
h2 {
  margin: 0 0 1em;
}
h3 {
  white-space: pre-line;
  font-size: 110%;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #600;
  line-height: 140%;
}
pre {
  padding: 0.4em;
  border: 1px solid #DAA;
  background: #FFFFF0;
  line-height: 110%;
  overflow: auto;
  max-height: 30em;
}
body>footer {
  border-top: 1px solid #DAA;
  padding: 0.8em 0 0;
  margin: 1em 0 0;
  font-size: 90%;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header><h1>ZptSharp rendering error</h1></header>
  <p class="user_message">
    Sorry, but an unexpected error occurred whilst getting the web page you requested.
    If this problem persists, please consider reporting it to the owner/maintainer of this website or application.
  </p>
  <section class="tech_info">
    <header><h2>Technical information</h2></header>
    <p>
      The following technical information may be useful to diagnose &amp; fix the error.
    </p>
    <h3 tal:content="here/Exception/Message">Unexpected exception whilst rendering a ZPT document as an MVC view.</h3>
    <pre tal:content="here/Exception">Exception stack trace
which may occupy
many lines</pre>
  </section>
  <footer>
    <div>
      ZptSharp v<span tal:replace="here/ZptVersion">v1.0.0</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      ZptSharp.Mvc5 v<span tal:replace="here/ZptMvcVersion">v1.0.0</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>